import React from 'react' import "../allcourses/courses.css" import { servicesCard } from "../../dummydata" import Title from '../common/title/Title' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' import { useTranslation } from 'react-i18next' const HAbout = () => { const [click, setClick] = useState(false); const [t] = useTranslation("global"); return ( <>
<div className='servicesCard'> {/* copy code form coursesCard */} <div className='grid2'> {servicesCard.slice(0, 6).map((val) => ( <div className='items'> <div className='content flex'> <div className='left'> <div className='img'> <img src={val.cover} alt='' /> </div> </div> <div className='text'> <h1>{t(`Habout.${val.serviceName}`)}</h1> <div className='rate'> <i className='fa fa-star'></i> <i className='fa fa-star'></i> <i className='fa fa-star'></i> <i className='fa fa-star'></i> <i className='fa fa-star'></i> <label htmlFor=''>(5.0)</label> </div> <div className='details'> <div className='para'> <h4>{t(`Habout.${val.detail}`)}</h4> <div className='blank'></div> <ul> {val.serviceList.map((l) => (<li>{t(`Habout.${l}`)}</li>))} </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div className='price'> <h3> {t(`price.${val.priceAll}`)} </h3> <h4>{t(`workDay.${val.workDay}`)}</h4> </div> <button className='outline-btn'>{t("Habout.quote")}</button> </div> ))} </div> </div> </div> </section> </> ) } export default HAbout
